Descriptions.Text: Looking for space, space and more space - then look no further!! Tucked away in the heart of this sought-after village, is this stunning individually designed family home with uninterrupted views of open countryside to the rear. The bespoke high quality finish is apparent from the moment you step in to the hallway with its solid oak staircase and underfloor heating, additionally the property comprises; bespoke fully fitted family kitchen, large entertaining dining room, grand formal lounge with inglenook fireplace. Snug / play room and additional study. To the first floor the large master bedroom benefits from the open views, dressing area and luxury en-suite. There is an en-suite to the guest bedroom and a Jack-and-Jill bathroom to bedroom three and four with an additional family bathroom. Externally to the front of the property is a private gravelled driveway providing ample off-street parking and leading to the integral mini garage. To the rear is a generous garden laid mainly to lawn with far reaching views over the rolling countryside.

Descriptions.Text: It's all about the location, location, location!! Situated in an elevated position on the extremely sought-after Bishopthorpe Road area of York and just a stones throw from the vibrant hustle and bustle of the eclectic mix of Bishopthorpe Road shops, Rowntree's Park, Millennium Bridge and 'outstanding' schools. This grand period property benefits from many original features and high ceilings throughout and briefly comprises; entrance hall, lounge, dining room, newly fitted breakfast kitchen, basement / den room with an extremely useful utility / laundry room, two double bedrooms and family bathroom to the first floor and two further double bedrooms and wet room to the 2nd floor. The property benefits from resident permit parking to the front and optional off-street parking to the rear of the property by separate negotiation. The front garden has been elegantly landscaped and to the rear, there is a secure garden with the addition of artificial grass making this garden, the perfect low maintenance outside space to accompany this fantastic city home.
